These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
City: berlin, london
1. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| City   | london | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
